name: sketch
description: After crossing the main suspended bridge,you will enter a narrow corridor that is twisted towards both sides along the way.Which gives shape to a hidden pathway.The walls here are tall and the ceiling has a reticular design which itergtates the lighting into this design throught the whole corridor.At the end of the corridor,suddenly you are met with a vast open area where different areas are linked by suspended bridges.All the bridges and pathways are at diffrent levels,therefore the end and the depth of the main area is not apparent.
